{"tid":1424630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實無傳媒知道聽日有民間記者會","createTime":"2019-08-06T16:13:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T16:46:56.000Z","uid":56802,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5ac5433b4ad1933a480b2dadd1efafa302742879","tid":1424630,"uid":56802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:13:16.000Z","msg":"搞記者會唔係出一次採訪通知就得架<br />\n如果係每日搞 你地要每日都出一次通知去各大傳媒<br />\n講明時間日期地點聯絡人<br />\n咁樣傳媒先派到人去架<br />\n而家傳媒其實係唔知聽日有記者會<br />\n成班連登仔係咁討論聽日點點點係㗰氣<br />\n如果真係有民間記者會 搞手快啲send通知啦<br />\n否則聽日無人嚟 變咗自己on99講野咋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"728a3e8fe891053e75e109908274c52a8ac614d0","tid":1424630,"uid":16765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:14:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7301bb689f0a65615a862facda9c1f7ccf65c6f1","tid":1424630,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:14:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c22bef171240c5ece8c17bbcfd017d9a5e6364f2","tid":1424630,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:15:57.000Z","msg":"聽日有咩？<br />\n真心唔知"},{"pid":"07383f9357c2f68ee9b07bec715019e631376440","tid":1424630,"uid":56802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:16:53.000Z","msg":"推 Media派緊聽日人手架啦 快啲出通知呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f76544c6f1652ed0c8b9